data.description: Welcome to your meticulously maintained single-story oasis in a coveted gated community! With only one owner ever, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spanning 1,353 square feet offers a seamless blend of comfort and style. Enjoy an open floor plan with a modern kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, a cozy living area, and a tranquil master suite with an en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Outside, discover your own private retreat with a new deck in the backyard, perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining. Take advantage of community amenities including a pool and park, all while being conveniently located near shopping, dining, and easy access to 1604. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity-schedule your showing today!--
